        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:04",
        "text": "Yes way!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:04",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "It's time for"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:07",
        "text": "News for kids"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:07",
        "end_time": "0:08",
        "text": "News for kids"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:08",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:11",
        "end_time": "0:13",
        "text": "原來是原來的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:14",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "你不知道的趣味新鮮事"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:19",
        "text": "ICRT News for kids"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:21",
        "end_time": "0:25",
        "text": "Are mobile phones the most important thing kids have?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:26",
        "end_time": "0:29",
        "text": "手機對小朋友來說很重要嗎?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:29",
        "end_time": "0:32",
        "text": "England's government doesn't think they are"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:32",
        "end_time": "0:34",
        "text": "With phones at school"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:34",
        "end_time": "0:36",
        "text": "Many kids can't study well."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:37",
        "end_time": "0:39",
        "text": "They don't talk very much to others."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:39",
        "end_time": "0:41",
        "text": "They sit and use their phones."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:42",
        "end_time": "0:48",
        "text": "英国很多小孩带手机上学,让他们没办法专心上课。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:48",
        "end_time": "0:52",
        "text": "他们也不怎么一起聊天,都坐着滑手机。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:53",
        "end_time": "0:56",
        "text": "So, England's government will have a new rule."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:57",
        "end_time": "0:59",
        "text": "Kids cannot use phones at school."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:00",
        "end_time": "1:02",
        "text": "They cannot use phones in class."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:02",
        "end_time": "1:05",
        "text": "They cannot use them during breaks."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:06",
        "end_time": "1:12",
        "text": "This means no phones between classes and no phones at lunch time."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:12",
        "end_time": "1:19",
        "text": "英国政府有了新规定,小朋友不可以在学校用手机。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:19",
        "end_time": "1:23",
        "text": "上课、下课跟吃饭时间都不可以用。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:24",
        "end_time": "1:27",
        "text": "Schools can decide what to do with phones."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:27",
        "end_time": "1:30",
        "text": "They can tell kids to leave their phones at home."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:43",
        "end_time": "1:47",
        "text": "學校可以決定怎麼處理手機。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:47",
        "end_time": "1:52",
        "text": "他們可以沒收,也可以要求學生把手機留在家裡。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:52",
        "end_time": "1:57",
        "text": "有的學校讓學生留著手機,但是不可以用。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:57",
        "end_time": "1:59",
        "text": "手機也要靜音。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:13",
        "end_time": "2:21",
        "text": "現在,很多學校都有手機規定,這個新規定可以讓兒童更認真上學嗎?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:22",
        "end_time": "2:28",
        "text": "有一些老師不這麼認為,覺得小朋友還是會在學校以外的地方用手機"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:28",
        "end_time": "2:33",
        "text": "Soon kids in England won't be using their phones at school."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:34",
        "end_time": "2:35",
        "text": "What do you think?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:35",
        "end_time": "2:37",
        "text": "Can this rule help you study better?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:39",
        "end_time": "2:40",
        "text": "Vocabulary"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:40",
        "end_time": "2:44",
        "text": "英國的學校對於手機有新的規定。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:44",
        "end_time": "2:46",
        "text": "Use 使用。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:46",
        "end_time": "2:49",
        "text": "Miss Lee, can I use my cell phone now?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:49",
        "end_time": "2:51",
        "text": "李老師,現在可以用手機嗎?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:52",
        "end_time": "2:54",
        "text": "Why do you need it, Lisa?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:54",
        "end_time": "2:56",
        "text": "為什麼你需要用呢,Lisa?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:57",
        "end_time": "2:58",
        "text": "Well, 好好的。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:59",
        "end_time": "3:03",
        "text": "因為我媽媽身體不舒服,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:05",
        "end_time": "3:07",
        "text": "我想要問問看她的情況。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:09",
